name: The Tower (digipack cd)
description:
We are proud to present you our third full lenght album "The Tower". The digipack cd edition comes with booklet and exclusive handcrafted coverart by our friend Costin Chioreanu.

To quote our label Season Of Mist:
"Money is power. This is truth and the theme of VULTURE INDUSTRIES’ twisted new album, “The Tower”. The Norwegians’ new full-length explores dark musical vistas and lyrics within a unique mixture of progressive, experimental, extreme and even foreboding symphonic elements. With a wealth of creativity and the ability to shift gears smoothly in the blink of an eye, VULTURE INDUSTRIES bend, twist, and shape their songs into living entities embodying the width and breadth of human emotion. Comparisons to unique and trail-blazing artists such as FAITH NO MORE, DEVIN TOWNSEND, ENSLAVED and NICK CAVE, only act as starting points to this unique heavy rock band. Welcome to one of the best records of 2013. Welcome to “The Tower”.
